videos.description: After playing his first career game against LeBron James, Lonzo Ball reacts to playing against his childhood idol, calling LeBron "the best player in the world."

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Interview (Lonzo reflects on matchup with LeBron) 2017/12/14

videos.headline: Lonzo reflects on matchup with LeBron

videos.description: Following their first career matchup, LeBron James calls Lonzo Ball a "really good player" and says he was "humbled" by being Lonzo's favorite player.
